{"tid":1506183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關心黑警仔女無問題，但要分清係咪自己友","createTime":"2019-08-25T17:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T17:39:43.000Z","uid":78241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4a98c648421f4dd4184e3177b99aea13d14a34d7","tid":1506183,"uid":78241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:32:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"889f0492e57b6a58a80ae7d9c042b2227ff3a980","tid":1506183,"uid":257422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:33:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[ 國際關係戰線 ]<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 為左亞馬遜森林，<br />\n麻煩香港人即刻同我戒食牛！<br />\n立即發起&quot;戒食牛行動&quot;文宣</span><br />\n香港仲要係入口牛肉最多既地方！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505744\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505744</a></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xVk3psM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxVk3psM.jpg&h=4050b9a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中港食客無牛不歡　禍延雨林</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190825/20755525\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190825%2F20755525&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxs%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=e448ac09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190825%2F20755525&h=66b84008\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190825/20755525</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2zFiXAR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2zFiXAR.png&h=62deb993&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">The Amazon is burning because the world eats so much meat</span><br />\nBy Eliza Mackintosh, CNN<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/2019/08/23/americas/brazil-beef-amazon-rainforest-fire-intl/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2019%2F08%2F23%2Famericas%2Fbrazil-beef-amazon-rainforest-fire-intl%2Findex.html&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxs%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=636548aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2019%2F08%2F23%2Famericas%2Fbrazil-beef-amazon-rainforest-fire-intl%2Findex.html&h=216c3621\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnn.com/2019/08/23/americas/brazil-beef-amazon-rainforest-fire-intl/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當大家打緊國際輸出革命，全球各國都幫緊香港人發聲既時候，另一單近期最大既新聞就係亞馬遜森林火燭，而香港竟然係入口最多牛肉既地方？？？<br />\n<br />\n唔該，依家香港軟實力啱啱先建立到，出國同人講自己係香港人，人地都會知你係民主鬥士，你唔會想又加返條破壞環境既罪名呀嘛？ 就算無人怪香港人，依個都係再次展現香港人人性光輝既重要機會！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知香港其實只係做轉口港，但做PR 唔好淨係成日掛住理真相係點<br />\n<br />\n政治d睇件事，如果香港人肯發起戒食牛行動到全世界都知道，今次會係一個為香港人branding既絕佳輸出革命機會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">即刻發起戒食牛肉行動！！！！<br />\n以示香港人面向國際，對國際社會既責任感！！！！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c70b994d11384d195445a059a0d8bfccf34419","tid":1506183,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:34:34.000